trans-unit.source: Represents a single [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element in an [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project.

trans-unit.target: 将指定的[任务](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)元素[目标](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)元素。

trans-unit.target: `Condition`属性的值`Target`元素。

trans-unit.target: `DependsOnTargets`属性的值`Target`元素。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the items that are to be input into this target.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置其输入到此目标的项。

trans-unit.source: Items inside this target attribute are used as the inputs in the top level dependency analysis.
trans-unit.target: 此目标属性内的项用作顶级依赖项分析中的输入。

trans-unit.source: A string representing the items.
trans-unit.target: 表示项的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element was imported into the project.
trans-unit.target: 获取一个值，该值指示是否[目标](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)元素已导入项目。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the `Target` element was imported into the project; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果`Target`元素已导入项目中; 否则为<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Gets the `Name` attribute value of the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.
trans-unit.target: 获取`Name`属性的值[目标](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)元素。

trans-unit.source: The `Name` attribute value of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: `Name`属性的值`Target`元素。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the expected outputs of this target.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置此目标的预期的输出。

trans-unit.source: You can apply transforms to this target attribute to transform a set of input items into a set of output items.
trans-unit.target: 可以将转换应用于此目标属性，可将一组输入项转换为一组输出项。

trans-unit.source: This attribute is used not only for top level dependency analysis but also for the purposes of defining this targets outputs.
trans-unit.target: 不仅为顶级依赖项分析，也用于定义此目标输出的目的使用此属性。

trans-unit.source: A string representing the outputs.
trans-unit.target: 表示输出的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified [Task](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element from the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.
trans-unit.target: 中移除指定[任务](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)元素从[目标](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)元素。
